“Save the best for last” they say. @valihoell certainly did 💪. After a long summer of bad luck, the young Austrian 🇦🇹 laid down a flawless & fast enough run for her 1st ever elite World Cup win 👏🎉.

Watch the full replay of today’s racing on Red Bull TV 👉 bio.
